Class Shop

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.util.Observable
      • be.ac.ulb.infof307.g10.models.AbstractObject
        • be.ac.ulb.infof307.g10.models.NamedObject
          • be.ac.ulb.infof307.g10.models.Shop
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable

    @Entity
public class Shop
extends NamedObject
    Class representing a shop. It is defined by a name, a stock, a schedule, a latitude and a longitude. His primary keys in the db are the name, the longitude and the latitude. It defines when a shop is unique.
